      <p id="Par39">We train the scBFA model by optimizing the following penalized likelihood function:
<disp-formula id="Equc"><alternatives><tex-math id="M19">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
