      <p id="Par63">The distinction between our simulation framework and ZINB-WaVE is that ZINB-WaVE maintains the same cell embedding space <inline-formula id="IEq24"><alternatives><tex-math id="M69">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
